<div class = "row ">
  <div class = "large-4 columns">
    <%=image_tag("Pakistaninvestinnutrition.jpg", alt: "Pakistan invest in nutrition", title: "Pakistan invest in nutrition")%>

  </div>
  <div class = "large-8 columns">
    <p><b>Budget Advocacy</b> –SUN CSAs are undertaking budget tracking to monitor government spending on nutrition. They are using this data in their advocacy to increase financial commitments towards tackling malnutriton.</p>
        <p> <b>Case study: Pakistan</b> – In Pakistan, the civil society alliance undertook Federal and Provincial budget analysis to track spending on nutrition. As part of their #Investinnutrition campaign, they used this data to lobby parliamentarians and to secure mass media coverage as well. As a result the Sindh government announced an allocation of one billion PKR to nutrition interventions annually for the next 3 years and the Federal Government allocated 100 million PKR for nutrition projects for the federal capital territory. </p>
  </div>
</div>
