    <p> <b>Case Study: Tanzania</b> –PANITA, the SUN Civil Society Alliance in Tanzania, launched the ‘Journalist Excellence in Reporting on Nutrition’ award to incentivise more reporting on nutrition issues. The alliance held an awards ceremony with the Deputy Minister for Information, Culture, Arts and Sports as the guest of honour.</p>
